outputs.output_descr: The project aims at advising the Brazilian Government on demands related to the Federal Government Strategic Programs, such as the Brazil without Poverty Plan (eradication of extreme poverty), programs related to the Millennium Development Goals and activities related to the United Nations Conference on Sustainable Development - Rio+20.
